These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, water
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: romance, drama
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: lacrosse, rugby
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, skateboard
1. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
2. the person drinking water is in an even position##4
3. the person watching drama movies is the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | almond-milk  | water   |
| Movie-Genre   | drama     | romance   |
| Sport         | rugby | lacrosse |
| Transport     | roller | skateboard    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: corn, lettuce
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: horror, fantasy
2 different pets are kept: turtle, mouse
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, snowmobile
1. the owner of the mouse is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching horror movies is the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | corn     | lettuce |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | horror  |
| Pet           | mouse         | turtle     |
| Transport     | ship   | snowmobile    |

 #################################

 
