2. the owner of the bird is on the right of the videographer##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Beverage    | coffee     | lemonade |
| Job         | videographer | pilot    |
| Pet         | goldfish         | bird        |
| Transport   | jet-ski         | train    |

