.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  pilot, mechanic
There are 2 different nationalities: pakistani, turkish
2 different pets are kept: goat, hedgehog
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: weightlifting, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in an even position##4
2. the turkish is on the far left or far right##3
3. the mechanic is the pakistani##1
4. the owner of the goat is on the left of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Job           | mechanic | pilot    |
| Nationality   | pakistani       | turkish |
| Pet           | goat         | hedgehog    |
| Sport         | weightlifting    | ice-hockey   |

